@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "CV Parser" as CVParser
participant "Screening Questions Module" as ScreeningQuestionsModule
participant "Rating and Scoring Module" as RatingandScoringModule
participant "User Interface Module" as UserInterfaceModule
participant "Natural Language Processing (NLP) Module" as NaturalLanguageProcessingNLPModule
participant "Similarity Calculation Module" as SimilarityCalculationModule
participant "ChatGPT Integration Module" as ChatGPTIntegrationModule
participant "Recruiter Dashboard Module" as RecruiterDashboardModule
UserInterfaceModule ->> CVParser : Submit CV for Parsing
CVParser -> ScreeningQuestionsModule : Trigger Screening Questions
ScreeningQuestionsModule -> UserInterfaceModule : Present Screening Questions
UserInterfaceModule ->> ScreeningQuestionsModule : Submit Applicant Responses
ScreeningQuestionsModule -> RatingandScoringModule : Trigger Rating and Scoring
CVParser -> RatingandScoringModule : Provide Parsed CV Data
NaturalLanguageProcessingNLPModule -> RatingandScoringModule : Provide NLP Data
SimilarityCalculationModule -> RatingandScoringModule : Provide Similarity Calculation Data
ChatGPTIntegrationModule -> RatingandScoringModule : Provide ChatGPT Score
RatingandScoringModule -> UserInterfaceModule : Provide Rating Result
UserInterfaceModule -> RecruiterDashboardModule : Trigger Recruiter Dashboard Update
ScreeningQuestionsModule -> RecruiterDashboardModule : Trigger Recruiter Dashboard Update
RatingandScoringModule -> RecruiterDashboardModule : Provide Rating Result
@enduml